name: GuardPath TM Managed Decumulation 2042 Fund
longDescription: The investment objective of the ETF is to make consistent, high monthly distributions over a twenty (20) year period. Fund investing the ETF's assets in a well-diversified portfolio of assets selected to achieve income generation and preservation of capital while minimizing overall volatility of returns.
